{"tid":1925280,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[ 監察左膠 ] 蔡耀昌辭任民主黨全部職務並獲接納","createTime":"2020-03-14T09:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T21:18:25.000Z","uid":21470,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7a651a47f89de955747810afaee5127b755f14cb","tid":1925280,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:13:58.000Z","msg":"蔡耀昌辭任民主黨全部職務並獲接納<br />\n<br />\n本身是民主黨中委蔡耀昌，日前以社區組織協會幹事身份，批評有食肆不招待內地旅客，是歧視行為，並要求平機會調查。民主黨表示，蔡耀昌下午在中委會會議聆聽所有意見後，主動提出辭任黨內全部職務，包括中委會、選舉委員會、財務委員會、章程委員會，並獲即時接納，中委會感謝蔡耀昌多年來貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨說，面對政府無能，商戶採取合理防疫措施，拒絕高風險人士光顧，並不涉及任何歧視行為，他們尊重及支持有關防疫舉動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1273651&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1273651%26csid%3D261_341&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCTsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=f3d74d64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1273651&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"b61f2759221329bf7b1c5e3c1a789171119e7c4b","tid":1925280,"uid":189799,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:24:39.000Z","msg":"退出埋民主黨啦"},{"pid":"3cc6c9901a8c1d80f5034777447a36ae7d0881aa","tid":1925280,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:25:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b9d4e77ea49c9a53767438b44da5737cb42f0df","tid":1925280,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T19:30:15.000Z","msg":"呢個卜街幫新移民爭福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />01講"},{"pid":"bb38cf68fc1f875a2b9d4aab12b3b6e7bd33db36","tid":1925280,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T20:33:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">為蔡耀昌申冤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1925265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http